Best way to find a good weapon in your price range is to sit in your local server main trade zone, and see what they auction out.<br>
On Veeshan its in North Freeport but it differs from server to server. On some its the tunnel in WC and i hear that on some its even Gfay, go figure =).and see what they auction out.<br>
A few things to think about though are that before lvl 20.. all weapons are capped at dmg 15 i think. so don't go for something with a huge amount of dmg before passing lvl 20.<br>
And to your comment that you prefer 2hs, well while 2h weapons can be nice you should at least dual wield enough to keep that skill maxxed for each lvl (this will really pay of at later lvls, where a warrior is much better of with 1hand weapons).<br>
And another thing that cant be stressed to hard is that you should do the same with all the weapons skills, keep a weapon of each type (1hb,1hs,piercing, 2hs and 2hb if you can) in your backpack and use them to keep them skills as high as you can.<br>
